@base = http://localhost:5000/api
@adminToken = Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_HERE

### Public read (storefront — no Authorization)
GET {{base}}/settings

### Admin update branding only (requires admin role JWT)
PUT {{base}}/settings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

{
  "websiteName": "Zippyyy"
}

### Clear logo URL (same as PUT /admin/settings with websiteLogoUrl: "")
PUT {{base}}/settings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

{
  "logo": ""
}

### Upload logo / favicon: POST {{base}}/admin/settings/upload-logo or upload-favicon
### Multipart form field name: file (use Postman or curl; do not set Content-Type manually).
